"1  French bread baguette, cut into 1/2-inch slices","2 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil","4 ounces cream cheese, softened","1/2 teaspoon lemon zest","1 tablespoon fresh lemon juice","1/2 teaspoon kosher salt","2 1/2 tablespoons chopped fresh dill, divided","1  English cucumber, thinly sliced","4 ounces smoked salmon","1/4 teaspoon cracked black pepper"